ta-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2530413\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nsv1665702982422.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nsv1665702982422.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nsv1665702982422.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nsv1665702982422\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Graphics Mode Mnemonics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The graphics mode set and rest mnemonics in the graphics mode for displays that\n    support them graphics mode. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__section_vpp_mzn_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221387e51\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Mnemonics for Setting Graphics Mode</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1__entry__2\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">_close</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1__entry__2\">Reset device from graphics mode. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">_init</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nsv1665702982422__table_d5600e1_d5601e1_d5602e1__entry__2\">Initialize device in graphics mode. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__section_y3z_nzn_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221387e113\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__p_d63971e1_d63972e1_d63973e1\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">init</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">close</code> are\n        also defined, these are activated before and after <code class=\"ph codeph\">_underscore, _inverse,\n          _high</code>, and so on, to invoke and cancel graphics mode.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__p_d63974e1_d63975e1_d63976e1\">These mnemonics are not used for printers.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"nsv1665702982422__pre_hk4_rzn_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^027=^027P1pW(R)S(C1(H0))W(F15)T’ ^_INIT\n’^027/ ^_CLOSE\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dcn1665702982352.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Session Mnemonics</a><p>These mnemonics start and end a session.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bbb1665702981995.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Secondary Process Color and Video Mnemonics</a><p>The secondary process mnemonics instruct Uniface to perform the video feature in a secondary print or display process, that is, by printing the line a second time.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530413\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530413\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Graphics Mode Mnemonics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Graphics Mode Mnemonics The graphics mode set and rest mnemonics in the graphics mode for displays that support them graphics mode. Arguments Table 1. Mnemonics for Setting Graphics Mode Mnemonic Explanation _close Reset device from graphics mode. _init Initialize device in graphics mode. Description If init and close are also defined, these are activated before and after _underscore, _inverse, _high , and so on, to invoke and cancel graphics mode. These mnemonics are not used for printers. ^027=^027P1pW(R)S(C1(H0))W(F15)T’ ^_INIT ’^027/ ^_CLOSE Copy Related Links Session Mnemonics These mnemonics start and end a session. Secondary Process Color and Video Mnemonics The secondary process mnemonics instruct Uniface to perform the video feature in a secondary print or display process, that is, by printing the line a second time. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}